{"tid":1432983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實民間記者會可唔可能....","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T13:46:36.000Z","uid":250134,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"420596af97813c79b585f26fdc370a35d8d62812","tid":1432983,"uid":250134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:16:21.000Z","msg":"其實民間記者會可唔可能....請到利君雅主持？<br />\n帶住口罩，以香港人身份讀出講稿？"},{"pid":"8b16b75f025634c29c22f8178bd6458b36cedb16","tid":1432983,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:18:41.000Z","msg":"8.9       機場萬人接機<br />\n開始時間： 2019年8月9日下午1 點起<br />\n地點 ： 一號客運大樓機場接機大堂<br />\n1. 不申請不反對通知書<br />\n2. 和平靜坐，不衝擊不破壞不入禁區<br />\n3. Be water<br />\n4. 促政府答應五大訴求<br />\n5. 停止暴力打壓示威遊行<br />\n少你一個真係少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日 機場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xGQPZ5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxGQPZ5c.png&h=7a7f7945&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c216143f75b3f65211807231b01d38c83f3901c","tid":1432983,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:26:03.000Z","msg":"Good idea.<br />\n<br />\n另外，針對<span style=\"color: blue;\">警方記招</span>的最強還拖兼宣傳運動，應該就係<span style=\"color: gold;\">民間記者會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家將對<span style=\"color: blue;\">警方記招</span>嘅討論帶到去<span style=\"color: gold;\">民間記者會</span>，咁就可以踩住警犬上。<br />\n<br />\n政府每日幾場記者會佔每日幾個鐘airtime同press編幅，咁樣係直接佔有緊民間話語權。<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋不如多啲討論返點樣改善同好好利用<span style=\"color: gold;\">民間記者會</span>"},{"pid":"0e49a1665355f1119ecbb7a0723cd8d1bcd1b899","tid":1432983,"uid":27349,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:29:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cf94b42c2ecf57765aafab24a14d650b5fa2fb8","tid":1432983,"uid":250134,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0e49a1665355f1119ecbb7a0723cd8d1bcd1b899","tid":1432983,"ui