當人on9?"},{"pid":"4cef88aae91126c517bae6a1c3fd3083b1b3339d","tid":1432983,"uid":111271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:21:24.000Z","msg":"如果因為佢敢言識講野要搵佢就收一收皮先  大把人都做到<br />\n定係因為佢出左名有光環所以要搵佢?<br />\n一陣令到佢比人搞記者都做唔到就真係多得你唔小<br />\n同埋佢真係好易比人認到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6218e18afafb3897abba5e8148e04060d7272af2","tid":1432983,"uid":13349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2150eda932135f9e84a2bea28c5876c20e21a9a0","tid":1432983,"uid":54415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:24:27.000Z","msg":"記者係要保持中立, 搵利君雅不如搵柳爺仲好, 起碼唔係傳媒界<br />\n同埋,唔覺得要有名人去做, 始終代表既係一眾反對派既聲音, 唔係個人既身份<br />\nBTW柳爺都係左膠+和理非"},{"pid":"748fadf7e3f9542f2eee71b68b3f28b588edb7cf","tid":1432983,"uid":27349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}